FeedPackage.Description:
This library provides a simple business object framework for creating rich business objects using Linq to SQL and Entity Framework (Code First). The library provides CRUD operations, context lifetime management, update error management, code based validation, free form property collection support and much more.
Both Linq to SQL and Entity Frameworks use the same methodology so code written for either Microsoft framework is easily portable between the two.
FeedPackage.Summary: A simple business object framework that wraps Linq to SQL and Entity Frameworks
FeedPackage.Tags: Westwind Linq to SQL Entity Framework CodeFirst Business Object
FeedPackage.Title: Westwind.BusinessFramework

FeedPackage.Description:
Provides a base business class layer for Linq to Sql and Entity Framework. The business classes encapsulate CRUD operations and manages the data context for L2S and EF, as well as providing low level helpers for non-supported data operations in L2S and EF among other things. Provides a great way to isolate your business logic into classes that consolidate functions related to your data entities.
Both Linq to SQL and Entity Frameworks use the same methodology so code written for either Microsoft framework is easily portable between the two.
